Motif de votre visite, Mr. Johnson?

67
00:08:49,339 --> 00:08:50,328
Business.

68
00:08:50,907 --> 00:08:52,135
Quel genre business?

69
00:08:52,742 --> 00:08:54,539
Protection environnementale.

70
00:09:01,451 --> 00:09:02,543
Merci.

71
